  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n  [*] --> Calm\n  Calm --> Aggressive: sees player (FOV + LOS)\n  Aggressive --> Alerted: player not seen (start cooldown)\n  Alerted --> Calm: cooldown elapsed\n  Alerted --> Aggressive: player seen again\n\n  note right of Aggressive\n    NPCPathSystem chases player\n    (repath interval)\n  end note\n\n  note right of Alerted\n    NPCPathSystem goes to last seen position\n  end note\n\n  note right of Calm\n    NPCPathSystem patrols between nodes\n    random idle 3-5s\n  end note\n",
  "content_size": 486,
  "collected_at": "2026-02-06T10:38:01.179615",
  "compilation_status": "success",
  "license": "other_source",
  "license_name": "Other Source (GitHub-based)",
  "compilation_error": "",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个NPC的状态机，核心是三种状态：平静、激进和警觉。初始状态是平静，当NPC在视野范围内且视线无遮挡看到玩家时，就切换到激进状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Calm",
        "Aggressive",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以触发条件是\"sees player (FOV + LOS)\"对吧？那激进状态回到警觉的逻辑是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggressive",
        "Alerted",
        "FOV + LOS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，当玩家脱离视野时，激进状态转为警觉，这时候要启动一个冷却计时器。如果冷却结束还没看到玩家，就回到平静；如果在冷却期间重新看到玩家，直接回到激进。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggressive",
        "Alerted",
        "Calm",
        "start cooldown",
        "cooldown elapsed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以警觉有两个出口：冷却结束回平静，或者再次看到玩家回激进。我先把这三个状态和四条转换画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alerted",
        "Calm",
        "Aggressive",
        "player seen again",
        "cooldown elapsed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "状态图画好了。现在需要给每个状态加上NPCPathSystem的行为说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NPCPathSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要的。激进状态时NPCPathSystem要追逐玩家，有个寻路重算间隔；警觉状态时去最后看到玩家的位置；平静状态则是在节点间巡逻，随机空闲3到5秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NPCPathSystem",
        "repath interval",
        "last seen position",
        "patrols between nodes",
        "random idle 3-5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：三个状态的行为都用右侧注释框来放，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "note right of Aggressive",
        "note right of Alerted",
        "note right of Calm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样结构清晰。激进和警觉的注释都要提到NPCPathSystem，平静状态把巡逻和随机空闲都写进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "note right of Aggressive",
        "note right of Alerted",
        "note right of Calm",
        "NPCPathSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。状态机从初始进入平静，视野触发激进，丢失目标进警觉，冷却或再次发现玩家决定后续走向，每个状态的NPCPathSystem行为也都标注在右侧了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Calm",
        "Aggressive",
        "Alerted",
        "NPCPathSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
